# Assignments

Assignment resources contain information regarding the user's current SRS state and milestones with an associated subject.

## Get All Assignments

```shell
curl "<%= current_page.data.api_root_url %>/subjects"
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <api_token_here>"
  -H "Wanikani-Revision: <%= current_page.data.api_revision %>"
```

